[recv] {"type": "message_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Identifying array issues**\n\nI’ve run into an issue where `appendCompletedChunk` is treating the entire array length of 12 as buffered instead of just 3. So when I pass 2 and total size 14, it ends up copying all 12, including nulls, creating a result that’s too long. I need to either fill `firstChunk` completely or not append at all. To test the buffered chunks, maybe I should fill it with 12 strings using a simpler approach. A more manual method might work better than using `IntStream`.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0413b9d5f38050e00169f2e22c74d881a29a3133e9389b49cc\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp8uIwn6Uo_T0yllru5y7oh_r-HVFU1D9OolNiloS_vD0PNVS9Dm3DfmbQoXg7CkARZAChr8Z6YPag38Bebn9JeToaFJEeXQJTk1ph0uOj_d7mj2zXPrmSm2soHyeVRJ5XbAuVY6DbbnxAWek7qQGs_gd-alhC6Q4Q_4FL-vUui8aHu4cv8zsHWBNDmNHxDJZX4qKUM9stNp-sSURikEhpOx2e-hEK7hD59AE2sjTYaxsggoxzbLjVROjcmwHoFLSnVOi6GobEyocJNkWrpdMnFkh7ACXgQCidl4vX3dW7Jrq_JW3NVqHk5iQfFGzZ2qADHZhqRyIQZOFCz1BMDi1M3M8YJ3DrtnL-cQAiBopqZ73Byi3ikTaO7Pvk5vBER_CSg2CW9cpt30QlmCRL8PhCs4TcxuzH1WFz9zSzyz9RZhVWpXujjsdmRQOjcd_5r1h9q-UGX9YLqQfO-l_JDduCzAizGqr4KC7YkSru_Bi0G8zvmMFYwuJdNBCLsLw7Yph_FDpiXGkmLL1fyQ-CNMCa8vTl1PHl12sBmoDsHUDK423PavEGWiDtaJLUGrVFIDQdR9kbmhvUEOuSeB2IlORGQ1jDtCuNGWdj0DI1W4K4OtufBak_SLuxvHhyf1Da3OL04K8uEUZZy7OIsoQkYnnO4tvBsedlWT-vr3dh1FkmdYJKpbsZRwLO3d9pB2mNcaFF60W8JIXhFAFeCSBmHDFQeLHmcL749yTm5BkMDOEq2tJV_zUyNH-qoDgMyHkwM70mgawHClkYSyVWnxsrDvNVK7AI3Xn6adJ5gH21aDuKdYEMLXqlIXwTYNUpIBhucHkIFmA51B3uyxx976Ii9j1Gw9SbkEoGnKuEzb9UhNi_kUg7OwZ9DY_T7gAHIm2iF7_M8qL8jIYBdLCNw9xMPzFG7dX7r6_Ocarfu4GuXe_yHKaO8l2kyxWrvfLqhIkOsrHQOlRtr4timLNnYQr8ibZad-NVK22VE5BFPFLZl9Z_LIbbQgNsWoCyb6lygZdfNR-13yVn_l3pPQSgpOW5QRXd9zkN-Q4sj3xcordw-YbnR8GKFYzY3i24nlOcV1p-_OrprQZNaaF_TrnYztmuiK52o51jcfU9LEKjRInJPQoEfJEGNLOCHu38hyO1YG4peiyv3M0_y1Os1fIYibaNarnFt0p8X5zhEzgydxLRTthE2LBOzUXLlVTdHcgjIZLsotGFTfht5YAh-5aktxr46H9_U3CfVnB5a1oU